{
  "texts": [
    "These filtered features from DWT are passed on to the classifier using a Support Vector Machine.",
    "The reason it has been chosen is its capability of maximizing the margin between classes so that even in cases where the class boundaries do not have linear separability, a robust separation could be gotten.",
    "This approach has been found quite effective in diagnosing colorectal cancer since a very effective coping with complex and overlapping class distributions dealing with cases of polyps and hemorrhoids results.",
    "It promotes the utilization of the strong set of features provided by both the CNNs and the DWT through the SVM, making it highly accurate and robust; it hence plays an important role in the overall performance.",
    "The U-Net, considered one of the most admired architectures in biomedical imaging performs segmentation."
  ]
}